---
title: Freekeh Soup with Kale and Sweet Potatoes
description: It’s time to get freekeh! The wholesome grain is the perfect complement to the hearty kale and sweet potatoes in this soup. Its slightly smoky flavor gets amped up even further with the addition of curry powder and our Tunisian spice blend. You’ll start to swoon for all the fragrant aromatics emanating from the pot before even taking your first sip.
